photo.title: The Summit

description._content:
999 Green (southeast corner of Green and Jones)

The Summit was first mentioned in Tales of the City.  Prior to a tryst with Anna, Edgar Halcyon attended a cocktail party at the Summit with Frannie.  During the tryst, Anna shared with Edgar the story about Atlantis. 

The Summit appeared again in Significant Others.  By that time, Mary Ann and Brian were married and living on the 23rd floor.
